{"type": "article", "id": 23673, "title": "编程积木盒", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-11T08:24:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 38, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702154114GmFygKuzshTLkrJo.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是英国伦敦的开发团队 Primo 设计的编程积木盒，是该团队推出的最新款。它包括一个立方体机器人 Cubetto，一块编程板，16 个彩色的按钮，一张世界地图和一本故事书。4 种彩色按钮分别指示向前、向左、向右和功能函数，按照特定的顺序排列就能指示机器人达到地图上的一个位置，以此来锻炼小朋友的逻辑思维能力，产品目前正在众筹，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/primotoys/cubetto-hands-on-coding-for-girls-and-boys-aged-3?token=e3978e14\">这里是众筹链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154110SGEVBc954Zlf7MI8.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.71556122\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154111e6UcyVBRwgmz3I4r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154112GBz6ya7Jrm9hViLu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070215411361NIkVPjQXwTyzBo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154113y1koY4a5nARCwep8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}